Instructions: Saute onion, garlic, and ground beef in a pan. Add crushed tomatoes, salt, pepper, and herbs. Simmer for 45 minutes. Cook spaghetti according to package instructions. Serve bolognese sauce over spaghetti. Garnish with parmesan cheese.
Saute onion, garlic, and ginger in a pan. Add chicken, curry powder, turmeric, and coconut milk. Simmer for 20 minutes. Serve with rice or naan bread. Garnish with cilantro.
Saute beef and mushrooms in a pan. Add beef broth, mustard, and sour cream. Serve over egg noodles. Garnish with parsley.
Saute onion, garlic, and spinach in a pan. Layer noodles, spinach mixture, and ricotta cheese in a baking dish. Top with shredded mozzarella. Bake for 45 minutes.
Brown ground beef and onion in a pan. Add canned tomatoes, kidney beans, chili powder, and cumin. Simmer for 45 minutes.
Saute shrimp, garlic, and red pepper flakes in butter. Serve over pasta. Garnish with parsley. and lemon.
Saute ground beef, onion, and taco seasoning in a pan. Serve in taco shells. Top with lettuce, cheese, and salsa.
Roast beetroot in the oven for 45 minutes. Slice and serve with walnuts and goat cheese. Dress with olive oil, lemon juice, salt, and pepper.
Deep fry fish and potatoes in beer batter. Serve with tartar sauce and malt vinegar."
Saute chicken and chorizo in a pan. Add rice, saffron, and chicken broth. Simmer for 30 minutes. Add shrimp and peas. Cook for an additional 10 minutes.
